      "para_id": "Q002033.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nanaya , the lady with perfect allure , Sumu-El , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built her E-ituda , temple that fills her heart with joy in Urim ."
    }
